{"tid":292412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔點睇「只是在做自已」嘅人？","createTime":"2017-06-21T11:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T17:10:29.000Z","uid":121958,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5b09d7e8364936174667ad47b1911ea5644f9f3","tid":292412,"uid":121958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"發覺最近有好多呢類人<br />\n例子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/190422_d15dd8cc55c3548f763f4a4338de0ea7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F190422_d15dd8cc55c3548f763f4a4338de0ea7.jpg&h=35bc3085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：做得好，係保持真我，支持<br />\n負皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：反對"},{"pid":"3b32a7b1366138c43ffa5f61cf3cd3eb4e7d73a5","tid":292412,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:10:50.000Z","msg":"其實佢除左打左句「做自己不改變之外」<br />\n邊忽睇到佢做自己?"},{"pid":"2cc8b561074bc80e3a93afb488d46e9359cec64c","tid":292412,"uid":121958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢除左打左句「做自己不改變之外」<br />\n邊忽睇到佢做自己?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔理佢做唔做到，價值觀上佢係咁諗"},{"pid":"ea6dc64c2adc1ed7c3e3d3bb86f067d13258c930","tid":292412,"uid":121958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c5897fa4af4dc81e07a5ba2cf27f77cab7810a","tid":292412,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"借刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fad77809c77af76a9cb748156cbf5d2200334f","tid":292412,"uid":3261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"活在自己世界，呢啲人拎去人道毀滅算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8841004d5ced1810e89682563839960063ac6d53","tid":292412,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"樓主溝唔到人放人上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4e6339fb9fb47e1aafd2785a1e6b7141e229ea","tid":292412,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主溝唔到人放人上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4fefa16568339504a2bdd672ee371bce7d778c69","tid":292412,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"人地的生活理念關樓主你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢&quot;做自己&quot;有搞尻你?"},{"pid":"0843b337fc0dc06637a9a98a70b6d94503af1e3f","tid":292412,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"樓主學好D中文先啦"},{"pid":"15dd0519fb35126adde70c272fe9ad31637bb3d8","tid":292412,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"話雖如此，但網路由於有很安全的防護措施，所以通常會產生三種人。 <br />\n        第一種人會在網路上突顯其次要性格。 <br />\n        一般人應該具有多重性格，而在日常生活處世中，所展現的為主要性格。 <br />\n        次要性格很可能被壓抑，也很可能自己本身並未察覺有這種性格。 <br />\n        但在網路上，代表自己的，已不再是血肉之軀，而是一些英文字母。 <br />\n        少了所有的應酬與必要的應對進退，也少了很多利害關係。 <br />\n        於是豬羊變色，反而在刻意或不自覺的情況下，展現自己的次要性格。 <br />\n      <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n        第二種人會在網路上變成他&ldquo;希望&rdquo;成為的那種人。 <br />\n        人性千奇百怪，一定會有某些性格是妳特別欣賞與羨慕的。 <br />\n        但很可惜，這些性格未必為妳所擁有。 <br />\n        於是妳會很希望成為擁有這些性格的另一種人。 <br />\n        而網路正好提供這個機會，讓妳變成這種人。 <br />\n        舉例而言，平常沉默寡言的，在網路上可能會風趣健談。 <br />\n        而害羞文靜的，則很容易變成活潑大方。 <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n        第三種人會在網路上變成他&ldquo;不可能&rdquo;成為的那種人。 <br />\n        上帝是導演，牠指定你必須扮演的角色，不管妳喜不喜歡。 <br />\n        而網路上並沒有上帝，因此所有角色皆由妳自導自演。 <br />\n        於是妳很可能在網路上扮演妳日常生活中根本不可能扮演的角色。 <br />\n        舉例而言，妳若是女的，很可能會在網路上變成男人。反之亦然。 <br />\n        或者妳已30歲，很可能會在網路上裝成17歲的幼齒姑娘。反之亦然。 <br />\n        又或者妳明明是恐龍，很可能會在網路上以絕代佳人自居。反之亦然。"},{"pid":"a13bee24af5fd4a7752e8b6e957066a826624684","tid":292412,"uid":89337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主係咪特登？po張無開名既圖但係一search句野就搵到"},{"pid":"1c0aa3bcac2a12074a5ff73cd44169047ee2b5cf","tid":292412,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T18:15:54.000Z","msg":"做自己點解要專登四圍同人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a4ad43fd9881967ae8ffdf896daf776986839c","tid":292412,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T18:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f3afee6a786b8c251675e9d5c16b0836d6a5e0","tid":292412,"uid":51129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T19:14:34.000Z","msg":"有自己主見係好事<br />\n不過通常嗌得呢d口號嘅人都係無乜主見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606b99b8677704fea3564e8d80a2c78d0d07e489","tid":292412,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T20:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有自己主見係好事<br />\n不過通常嗌得呢d口號嘅人都係無乜主見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n提醒自己要做自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d309ce3a314e017e8f53459c30da8cf2d912dd3c","tid":292412,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T21:06:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ea13f2fbdf918437c7673b700bd17052fd2c1ba","tid":292412,"uid":121958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地的生活理念關樓主你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/de